QuestionTxt: Who do you think Russia wanted to win the (2016) presidential election--Hillary Clinton or Donald Trump?
StudyNote: 432 respondents were interviewed on a landline telephone, and 588 were interviewed on a cell phone. Interviews were conducted by Braun Research.
